{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Countryballs: Rise of Europe is a game that has two modes: strategic and sandbox. In the strategic mode, you play for the country, and must extract resources, for this you can build cities or deal with deforestation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428840/extras/resource_menu.jpg?t=1738015830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You also need to monitor the indicators of resources, because if you have a shortage of some resource, then crisis times will come and the country will become weak. You can also engage in the development of technology and expansion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428840/extras/impaire.jpg?t=1738015830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can build your own empire, but consider the fact that with the large size of the country in you will fall the level of military power (support) due to the fact that regions appear in your country that are not loyal to your government, but you can compensate for this by counting faster technology development. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428840/extras/map_editor.gif?t=1738015830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In sandbox mode (or observer) you are watching more countries for which AI plays. You can edit them: military power, form borders, force to attack other countries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also in the game there is a system of creating your own country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">music creator: Kevin MacLeod</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3428840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738015830","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/